node.text: In recent months, stadiums became a place to cast a vote in a consequential election, receive a vaccination against a deadly virus, or pick up a meal for a hungry family. #ItTakesAllofUs

node.title: NFL stadiums continue to serve as the heartbeat of our communities.

node.text:
Victor Cruz, Joey Bada$$, Marcedes Lewis, D Smoke, Xavien Howard, Rick Ross, and more. Introducing “NFL City Life.” 

Get to know NFL cities through the eyes and experiences of NFL players and local celebrities. Tune in to @NFLNetwork on 9/17 for episode one.
